    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained in impeccable showroom condition. This unit represents the zenith of automotive preservation, featuring a flawless exterior profile and an interior that remains in a pristine, original state. Meticulously curated and mechanically peerless, this vehicle offers an unrivaled driving experience for the discerning collector who demands nothing short of perfection. A rare acquisition for those seeking an investment-grade example of engineering excellence.",
