    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it's time for a new home. This car is in absolutely stunning condition\u2014seriously, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied this ride since day one, keeping it spotless and staying on top of every single service. It drives like an absolute dream and is ready for your next big road trip. You won't find another one this clean out there! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come see it in person!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
