    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 2010 Porsche 911 Carrera S (997.2) represents a pinnacle of analog engagement, featuring the 3.8L naturally aspirated flat-six with Direct Fuel Injection (DFI) delivering a linear 385 hp. The 6-speed manual transmission offers precise, tactile throws, paired with a factory-optioned limited-slip differential for optimal power delivery. This example boasts Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) with a 10mm lower ride height, ensuring surgical turn-in and high-speed stability. Mechanically impeccable, the chassis exhibits zero bushing deflection, and the braking system retains its factory-spec bite with four-piston monobloc calipers and cross-drilled rotors. Meticulously maintained with a documented service history and no over-rev entries, this is a turn-key, concours-standard specimen for the discerning purist.",
